    <item>
      <title>[바이낸스] Bybit, Mantle, Aave가 그리는 미래형 온체인 DeFi 유동성 생태계</title>
      <link>https://blockdailynews.online/news/2025/12/2025-12-02-bybit-mantle-and-aave-partner-to-bring-institutional-grade-d/</link>
